lead_paragraph: Marcus Stroman outpitched Chris Archer in his first opening day start, helping the Toronto Blue Jays begin defense of their first AL East title in 22 years with a 5-3 victory over the Tampa Bay Rays on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Stroman Solid in 1st Opening Day Start, Blue Jays Beat Rays
